{"id":10530,"type":6,"name":"The Mentalist (season 2)","name_cn":"超感神探 第二季","date":"2009-09-24","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/f3/e0/10530_KxAGY.jpg","rating":{"rank":828,"total":25,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":1,"7":8,"8":12,"9":2,"10":1},"score":7.6},"summary":"如今，从 \"名人圈\" 里 \"卸甲归田\" 的Jane当上了加利福尼亚调查局（CBI）专案调查组的独立顾问。他利用自己的\"超感\"特长连续破获了多起公众关注度高的疑难悬案，惊人的破案效率和成功记录让很多人连呼\"神人\"。但是在调查局内，大家都知道Jane的底细－－他是个缺乏纪律感、不愿意按规矩办事的家伙。\r\n　　古板严肃、一切只知道照本宣科的高级特工Teresa Lisbon (Robin Tunney, \"PrisonBreak\")拿Jane非常头疼－－一方面，她公开排斥Jane，认为他虚伪、自恋、华而不实，喜欢卖弄自己，不希望他留在自己的团队里。她尤其憎恨Jane公私不明、轻重不分的性格，认为他总有一天会威胁到所有人的安全。但另一方面，她也不得不承认：Jane的作用无人可替代，他的判断力对同事们来说非常有价值。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>超感神探 第二季</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>星期四</li><li><span>配角: </span><a href=\"/person/48411\">Malcolm McDowell</a>、<a href=\"/person/28673\">Taylor Gray</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>心计 第二季</li><li><span>集数: </span>23</li><li><span>开始: </span>2009-09-24</li><li><span>结束: </span>2010-05-20</li><li><span>类型: </span>刑侦</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>美国</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语</li><li><span>每集长: </span>40-43分钟</li><li><span>频道: </span>CBS</li><li><span>电视台: </span>CBS</li><li><span>首播国家: </span>美国</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>http://www.cbs.com/primetime/the_mentalist/</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>1474306</li><li><span>制片: </span>Bruno Heller</li><li><span>主演: </span>Simon Baker</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">主演: </span>Robin Tunney</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">主演: </span>Tim Kang</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">主演: </span>Owain Yeoman</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">主演: </span>Amanda Righetti</li>","collection":{"on_hold":2,"dropped":1,"wish":2,"collect":34,"doing":3},"tags":[{"name":"心理","count":8},{"name":"犯罪","count":6},{"name":"神棍","count":5},{"name":"CBS","count":5},{"name":"美剧","count":4},{"name":"卖萌白兔","count":3},{"name":"罪案","count":2},{"name":"派翠克","count":1},{"name":"剧情","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":61827,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/61827","type":